## Local Development

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone <repo_url>
cd enterprise-audio-pipeline
```

### Environment Variables

Create:

```bash
.env
```

Example:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=YOUR_GROQ_API_KEY

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@db:5432/audio_pipeline

REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379/0

MINIO_ENDPOINT=minio:9000
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=admin
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=password123

API_KEY=raksha_secure_key_999
```

---

### Start Services

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

Verify:

```bash
docker ps
```

Expected:

```text
postgres
redis
minio
api
worker
```

